  </h3>
  <h3 class="slider__presentation-bis"> Iris Crey is a multidisciplinary artist working in photography, iconographic citations, text and mixed medias. As a doctor in visual arts, she continues an investigation on the universality of sentiments, the subjectivity of representations and the ontological status of images.
